\" - Burke et al, 2018\nfits with a lot of other research that suggests a potentially extraordinary outcome for the current accidental random experiment on this planet's systems.\nFrom the abstract of the paper:\nBQSTART\nwe are effectively rewinding the climate clock by approximately 50 My, reversing a multimillion year cooling trend in less than two centuries.\nBQEND", "recommendation_count": "2", "in_reply_to": "125191140", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "125199131", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1548717315000}, "author": "takenisthis", "author_id": "17256959", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "This comment was removed by a moderator because it didn't abide by our\ncommunity standards.\nReplies may also be deleted. For more detail see our FAQs.", "causal_relations": [{"cause": "it did n't abide by our community standards", "effect": "this comment was removed by a moderator"}]}, {"id": "125193071", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1548705265000}, "author": "rockyrex", "author_id": "2923581", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "The U.S. Corn Belt is projected to experience a loss of 11% corn production per degree of warming\nSee Page 28 of that document.", "recommendation_count": "5", "in_reply_to": "125192579", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "125192938", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1548705022000}, "author": "Delius", "author_id": "2611744", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "You rather missed that she was aiming at humour here.", "recommendation_count": "4", "in_reply_to": "125191133", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "125199078", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1548717129000}, "author": "madmusician", "author_id": "17778772", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "I wonder - do you have children? The rate that ice is melting in Greenland may will start flooding London regularly by the end of this century - the ice is falling off in great lumps, lubricated by melted water underneath. No-one predicted 