ly as Australian conservative politicians are still inexplicably mute on the issue of serious emissions abatement and cessation.\nI weep for this island's future.", "recommendation_count": "23", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "125301522", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1548869095000}, "author": "Sonofabeach", "author_id": "15905104", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "Australians have been dealing with droughts, fires, flooding rains, cyclones and heat waves for over 250 years, so there\u2019s no need to concern yourself OpinionatedCanadian, we\u2019ll be just fine. 99.9% of the time our weather is divine. You should come down under for visit some time, after they\u2019ve reopened your airports which are closed due to record breaking cold. Take care mate eh.", "recommendation_count": "2", "in_reply_to": "125295037", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "125300605", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1548868091000}, "author": "Screamingman", "author_id": "18346738", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "Can\u2019t you Australians learn to rake the forests like the Finns do?", "recommendation_count": "9", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "125284449", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1548851067000}, "author": "PDGFD1", "author_id": "13011646", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "Thanks for this appearance Dog. Pretty sure everyone here has been checking throughout each day to see if you and yours are OK (bless Twitter too)\n 'Dogonaut Loungers' have been given a bit of a 'look in' to The Institute characters and workings over the years... you've all gone through so much to get to your piece of paradise ... but take your mob and go when you must. Might sound a bit odd from a total stranger, but youse guys are precious.\n May you, your 'Offsider', your menagerie and your garden all be safe from this monster.Rest assured there are those who will have your back if the worst happens.", "recommendation_count": "15", "causal_relations": nul