 the changes - but if everything is mismanaged then no-one can move forward. I think this is going to become more and more relevant - no matter what the outcomes are. Because by creating the space to make the changes necessary, then change will happen; and in many different ways. It will take time, but change will happen if good people are allowed to do the work they need to do.", "recommendation_count": "6", "causal_relations": [{"cause": "we are finding out that we can make changes with relatively minor inconvenience to most ordinary people if the right kind of policies are in place", "effect": "this is"}, {"cause": "these people act as a roadblock for change", "effect": "if we have a group of people at the top who are not engaging with the threat on any level then we all pay for the consequences the wrong government is the worst situation"}]}, {"id": "124927337", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1548080572000}, "author": "RichieRich66", "author_id": "1242820", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "This comment was removed by a moderator because it didn't abide by our\ncommunity standards.\nReplies may also be deleted. For more detail see our FAQs.", "causal_relations": [{"cause": "it did n't abide by our community standards", "effect": "this comment was removed by a moderator"}]}, {"id": "124926724", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1548079709000}, "author": "Brainingtree", "author_id": "15275664", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "i thought his main principle was how to spend money and that it should be on R&D of alternative energy.I understand he is a political scientist who works with economists.", "recommendation_count": "1", "in_reply_to": "124925509", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "124925509", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1548078005000}, "author": "DWilliams21x", "author_id": "101308278", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "I think he skips over a lot of important details. In effect, he doesn't believe the worst p