tems in pristine condition. The same cannot be said for the private operators. For example, Black Saturday bush-fires, some fires were started by poorly maintained power lines.\nBut how could the SEC have run a system cheaper and better than the current private operators, especially when we have been told repeatedly over the last 30 years that governments cannot do these things as well as private enterprise?\nTaken from this article:\nhttp://newsweekly.com.au/article.php?id=4292", "recommendation_count": "10", "in_reply_to": "125031490", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "125031845", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1548318786000}, "author": "familygardener2", "author_id": "17730933", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "That's a Pulitzer right there.", "recommendation_count": "3", "in_reply_to": "125031649", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "125032407", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1548320078000}, "author": "AwakenstoEmptiness", "author_id": "100031067", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "The thanks goes both ways.", "recommendation_count": "14", "in_reply_to": "125032190", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "125032382", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1548320023000}, "author": "TheParlormentOz", "author_id": "101240973", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "Stay alert, hydrated, safe, & cool y'all.", "recommendation_count": "8", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "125031296", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1548317437000}, "author": "D_K_4_8", "author_id": "14637422", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "It's actually a dark and brutal country song that I'm proud to be a part of.", "recommendation_count": "0", "in_reply_to": "125030166", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "125031294", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1548317436000}, "author": "TheParlormentOz", "author_id": "101240973", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "Something about a Victoria's Yallourn coal-fired power station having running only