ch? What environmental disaster will that leave behind elsewhere?", "recommendation_count": "0", "in_reply_to": "124746266", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "124754191", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1547682062000}, "author": "Gregory Shearman", "author_id": "14899696", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "I'm not talking about storms. I'm talking SWELL. How about coming here on the East Coast of Australia during a normal East Coast Low that we have about 3-4 times a year. The swells become mountains driven by the southern ocean swells. There is nothing comparable in the North Sea, just short sharp wind driven waves.\nBTW, we had a category 2 cyclone here in Newcastle a few years ago... now THAT's a storm.", "recommendation_count": "3", "in_reply_to": "124749334", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "124754185", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1547682054000}, "author": "Drfish", "author_id": "17210000", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "Anyone stupid enough to buy beachfront property in this day and age deserve to have it washed away from underneath them. Sorry, but the warnings have been there for decades, if they chose to ignore them then they shouldn't expect the taxpayer to foot the bill for their own stupidity. There are more important issues surrounding climate change to deal with than propping up failing real estate acquisitions.", "recommendation_count": "24", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "124756008", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1547686196000}, "author": "AwakenstoEmptiness", "author_id": "100031067", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "text": "What was not included in that parable in the bible is that the foolish man who built his house upon the sand simply petitioned the government for assistance.", "recommendation_count": "8", "causal_relations": null}, {"id": "124754158", "time_stamp": {"$date": 1547682016000}, "author": "Brad_Shannon", "author_id": "18510197", "schema_org_type": "http://schema.org/Comment", "te